Wash two cups yellow lentils
add 7 cups water, 2 Tbs olive oil
boil ~20 min/until soft

Sautee 
	- 2 Tbs olive oil
	- 2 Tbs mustard seed
	- chopped onion
	few minutes later
	add 1 Tbs ea./mix well
	- Tumeric
	- Cumin
	- Cayenne/similar

Combine lentils and other
S + P to taste
blend

Top with:
French fried onions
Sour Cream
Cilantro
Serano Chiles

